{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji35.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给孙燕的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给孙燕的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1955年8月3日）配君同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的信收到，很高兴。你们想到北京一看，是可以的；但是今年不要来，明年再说吧。你母亲在何处工作，情况如何？如有困难，可告知。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝你进步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五五年八月三日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]孙燕，学名孙配君。她的母亲陈玉英曾在毛泽东和杨开慧的家里当保姆。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1955,"month":8,"day":3}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":262,"page_end":262},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}